  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      117.38,
      407.56,
      481.57,
      423.1
    ],
    "text": "Advisory on Unnecessary Fuel Collection from Fuel Stations",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      437.68,
      511.49,
      485.38
    ],
    "text": "It has been observed that some members of the public are attempting to stockpile fuel due to concerns arising from the current adverse situation in the Middle East.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      499.96,
      517.11,
      531.58
    ],
    "text": "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation has confirmed that the island has sufficient fuel reserves, and there is no cause for undue panic.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      546.16,
      521.42,
      642.25
    ],
    "text": "However, as reports indicate that certain parties are collecting fuel in gallons or other external containers, all police stations have been instructed to coordinate with fuel station management to prevent such practices. Fuel should not be dispensed in gallons, bottles, or other containers, except for legitimate purposes such as fishing vessels, factories, workplaces, agricultural activities, and household use, until further notice.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      656.83,
      526.2,
      720.61
    ],
    "text": "The Sri Lanka Police will investigate and take legal action against individuals or groups involved in the unauthorized collection, storage, or resale of fuel at inflated prices, as well as those spreading false information on social media regarding fuel availability.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
